主派贏到區選，贏到既民主派議員，聽日唔使過嚟謝票，去poly用民意接被困嘅人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35aacc742738ba28d5839e377ee7a3d3efcccc1","tid":1751910,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:34:07.000Z","msg":"真心"},{"pid":"199c57ef5eed1fdb4d63ce8be24457a8e1e9656d","tid":1751910,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:34:23.000Z","msg":"發揮下你地用處"},{"pid":"70a5a82d021064e874d63ada9dcd2e599d1c6925","tid":1751910,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:35:42.000Z","msg":"推"}]}